== ActsAsEventable

ActsAsEventable makes it easy to log events corresponding to actions taken on active record models.

== Usage

in your controller (typically application_controller)

class FooController 
  record_events
  
  # or 
  
  record_events lambda { something_that_returns_a_user }
end

in your model

class FooModel
  acts_as_eventable
end


